service: event-logs-app

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  region: us-east-2

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

functions:
  registerEvent:
    handler: dist/lambdas/register-events.handler
    timeout: 30
    events:
      - http:
          path: events/register
          method: post
  getEvents:
    handler: dist/lambdas/get-events.handler
    timeout: 30
    events:
      - http:
          path: events
          method: get
